        // Masthead
        header.masthead.bg-primary.text-black.text-center
            .container.d-flex.align-items-center.flex-column
                // Masthead Avatar Image
                img.masthead-avatar.mb-5(src='assets/img/logo.webp', alt='Exporra logo — AI-powered export classification and sanction screening platform', width='225', height='225')
                // Masthead Heading
                h1.masthead-heading.text-uppercase.mb-0 Exporra
                // Icon Divider
                .divider-custom.divider
                    .divider-custom-line

                // Masthead Subheading
                p.masthead-subheading.font-weight-light.mb-0 AI-Powered Export Classification (ECCN &amp; HS Code) and Sanction Screening

   
        // What We Offer Section
        section#what-we-offer.page-section.bg-light.text-dark.mb-0
            .container
                // What We Offer Section Heading
                h2.page-section-heading.text-center.text-uppercase.text-dark Export Classification &amp; Sanction Screening, Automated
                // Icon Divider
                .divider-custom
                    .divider-custom-line

                //  What We Offer Section Content
                .row
                    .col-lg-12.mx-auto
                            ul.lead
                                
                                    strong Automated ECCN and HS Code Classification: 
                                    | Our AI-powered export classification tool assigns accurate Export Control Classification Numbers (ECCN) and Harmonized System (HS) codes to your products, saving time and minimizing costly errors.
                                    br
                            
                                    strong Continuous Sanctions &amp; Regulatory Monitoring: 
                                    | Stay updated on changes to OFAC, BIS, EU consolidated sanctions and UN sanctions lists, dual-use goods controls, and other export regulations that may impact your products.
                                    br
                            
                                    strong Sanction, Denied &amp; Restricted Party Screening: 
                                    | Run Know Your Customer (KYC), denied party screening and restricted party screening on customers and partners to detect sanctions risks before they become a problem.
                                    br
                            
                                    strong End-to-End Trade Compliance: 
                                    | Manage export classification, sanction screening and audit-ready compliance records from a single centralized platform — effortlessly.


        // How It Works Section
        section#how-it-works.page-section.bg-primary.text-black.mb-0
            .container
                // How It Works Section Heading
                h2.page-section-heading.text-center.text-uppercase.text-black How AI-Powered Export Classification &amp; Screening Works
                // Icon Divider
                .divider-custom.divider
                    .divider-custom-line

                //  How It Works Section Content
                .row
                    .col-lg-12.mx-auto
                            ul.lead
                                
                                    strong 1. AI-Powered ECCN and HS Code Classification
                            ul.lead-list
                                    | Exporra uses advanced large language models to analyze product data and automatically assign accurate ECCN classifications and HS codes. The system evaluates product descriptions, technical specifications, and dual-use goods regulations to ensure compliance with local and international export control laws.
                            ul.lead
                                    strong 2. Smart Data Consolidation
                            ul.lead-list
                                    | Exporra organizes and centralizes all product information into a structured, user-friendly database. Data is continuously updated, reducing administrative overhead and ensuring compliance information is always easily accessible.
                            ul.lead                     
                                    strong 3. KYC, Sanction &amp; Denied Party Screening
                            ul.lead-list
                                    | Exporra cross-references your customer and partner data with real-time updates from OFAC, BIS, EU consolidated sanctions, UN sanctions lists, embargoes and other restricted party lists. The platform’s AI monitors global compliance databases and regulatory changes. If updates impact your products or customers, you’ll receive immediate notifications with actionable insights, enabling you to respond swiftly and effectively.
                                    

        // Why Exporra Section
        section#why-exporra.page-section.bg-light.text-dark.mb-0
            .container
                // Why Exporra Section Heading
                h2.page-section-heading.text-center.text-uppercase.text-black Why Choose Exporra for Trade Compliance?
                // Icon Divider
                .divider-custom.divider
                    .divider-custom-line

                //  Why Exporra Section Content
                .row
                    .col-lg-12.mx-auto
                            ul.lead
                                
                                    strong Accuracy You Can Trust: 
                                    | Our AI-Powered tool doesn’t just automate—it double-checks classifications to ensure you meet international standards.
                                    br
                                  
                                    strong Risk Mitigation:
                                    | Stay ahead of potential compliance issues with proactive monitoring and alerts.
                                    br
                                
                                    strong Efficient Solutions:
                                    | Streamline compliance, reduce costs, and save valuable time, all while protecting your reputation.
                                    br
                                   
                                    strong Peace of Mind:
                                    | With Exporra, you can trust that your products are classified correctly and your processes are fully compliant.


        // Launch Section
        section#launch.page-section.bg-primary.text-dark.mb-0
            .container
                // Launch Section Heading
                h2.page-section-heading.text-center.text-uppercase.text-black Launch
                // Icon Divider
                .divider-custom.divider
                    .divider-custom-line

                // Launch Section Content
                .row
                    .col-lg-13.mx-auto
                        ul.lead
                            | The future of trade compliance is here.
                            strong Exporra 
                            | launches in 
                            strong June 2026
                            | , and we invite you to be part of this transformation.
                            br
                            | Interested in simplifying your compliance and reducing risks? 
                            br
                            | Contact us at 
                            a.text-black(href="mailto:Info@exporra.com") Info@exporra.com
                            |  to learn more or secure early access to our platform.




        // About Us Section
        section#about-us.page-section.bg-light.text-black.mb-0
            .container
                // About Us Section Heading
                h2.page-section-heading.text-center.text-uppercase.text-dark About Us
                // Icon Divider
                .divider-custom
                    .divider-custom-line

                // About Us Section Content
                .row
                    .col-lg-12.mx-auto
                        

                            ul.lead
                                strong   Driven by Excellence. United for a Safer World.
                            ul.lead
                                | At Exporra, we’re more than just a team. We’re a mission-driven family of expert programmers and experienced lawyers. Together, we’ve combined cutting-edge technology with deep regulatory expertise to create a platform that does more than streamline compliance.<br> 


        // Goals & Vision Section
        section#goals-vision.page-section.bg-primary.text-dark.mb-0
            .container
                // Goals & Vision Section Heading
                h2.page-section-heading.text-center.text-uppercase.text-dark Goals & Vision
                // Icon Divider
                .divider-custom
                    .divider-custom-line

                // Goals & Vision Section Content
                .row
                    .col-lg-12.mx-auto
                        


                        p.lead-paragraph Our goal is to help businesses:
                        ul.lead-list
                                li Stay ahead of complex global regulations.
                                li  Save time, resources, and money.
                                li Operate responsibly in an ever-changing world.

                        ul.lead
                                | But our vision goes beyond business. We believe in being
                                strong Warriors of Peace
                                |. 
                                br
                                | Every line of code and every compliance solution we design is built to ensure that products stay out of the wrong hands. By empowering companies to follow international regulations, we contribute to a safer world—one where trade fosters growth, not conflict.
                        ul.lead
                                | Every day, we work to build a platform that safeguards your business while supporting global stability and peace. 
                                br
                                | Because at Exporra, we’re not just solving problems; we’re creating solutions that matter.



    

